<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ hero_title_line1 }} · {{ hero_title_line2 }} — ISSUE #{{ issue_number }}</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@400;500;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0D0D0D;
      --surface: #161616;
      --surface-2: #1C1C1C;
      --text: #F5F5F5;
      --text-sub: #8A8A8A;
      --text-mute: #5A5A5A;
      --border: #2A2A2A;
      --accent: #FFA500;
      --accent-soft: rgba(255,165,0,0.08);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    html { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Pretendard Variable', Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px 80px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-feature-settings: 'ss02';
    }

    .serif {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', 'Nanum Myeongjo', serif;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* HEADER - Hero style (2줄 세리프 거대 타이틀 + 대각선 스트라이프 악센트 바) */
    header {
      padding: 64px 0 0;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    header h1 {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 72px;
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    header h1 .line {
      display: block;
    }
    header .meta-line {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      font-feature-settings: 'tnum';
    }
    header .meta-line .issue {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    header .meta-line .dot {
      color: var(--text-mute);
    }
    header .accent-bar {
      height: 10px;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        -45deg,
        var(--accent) 0, var(--accent) 12px,
        var(--bg) 12px, var(--bg) 18px
      );
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .trending {
      color: var(--text-mute);
      font-size: 13px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 4px 14px;
      align-items: baseline;
    }
    .trending .label {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }
    .trending span.tag {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    /* 꼭 알아야 할 뉴스 — 전체 엠버 블록 배너 (검정 타이포 · 900 weight · 0.18em spacing) */
    .must-read {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--bg);
      border-left: none;
      padding: 26px 22px;
      margin: 0 -20px 48px;
    }
    .must-read h2 {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--bg);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .must-read .item {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .must-read .item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .must-read .item h3 {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
      color: var(--bg);
    }
    .must-read .item .meta {
      color: var(--bg);
      font-size: 12px;
      opacity: 0.75;
    }
    .must-read .item .meta .score {
      color: var(--bg);
      font-weight: 700;
      opacity: 1;
      font-feature-settings: 'tnum';
    }
    .must-read .item a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* 카테고리 섹션 — Surface box with sticky header + 2px 엠버 테두리 + 12px 라운드 */
    .section {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-top: 28px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 2px solid var(--accent);
    }
    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--bg);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }
    .section-header h2 {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      color: var(--bg);
    }
    .section-header .count {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-feature-settings: 'tnum';
      font-weight: 800;
      padding: 4px 12px;
    }
    .section-body {
      padding: 4px 22px 8px;
    }

    /* Article card (full info) */
    .article {
      padding: 20px 0 28px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .article:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .article h3 {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
      font-size: 19px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    }
    .article h3 a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .article .meta {
      color: var(--text-sub);
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .article .meta .dot { color: var(--text-mute); }
    .article .meta .score {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-feature-settings: 'tnum';
    }
    .article .tags {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-mute);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .article .why {
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
      padding: 9px 13px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      border-radius: 0 3px 3px 0;
    }
    .article .why strong {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-right: 4px;
    }

    /* 인사이트 토글 — <details> 기반, JS 불필요 */
    .article .why-insights {
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: 0 3px 3px 0;
      padding: 9px 13px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }
    .article .why-insights > summary.why {
      background: transparent;
      border-left: 0;
      padding: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0;
      cursor: pointer;
      list-style: none;
      border-radius: 0;
    }
    .article .why-insights > summary.why::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .article .why-insights > summary.why::marker { content: ""; }
    .article .why-insights .expand-hint {
      margin-left: 8px;
      color: var(--accent);
      transition: transform 0.2s;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .article .why-insights[open] > summary.why .expand-hint { transform: rotate(180deg); }
    .article .why-insights .insights-body {
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding-top: 10px;
      border-top: 1px dashed var(--border);
    }
    .article .why-insights .insight { margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .article .why-insights .insight:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .article .why-insights .insight h4 {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }
    .article .why-insights .insight p {
      font-size: 13.5px;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .article .summary {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .article .link {
      color: var(--text-sub);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 13px;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }
    .article .link:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    footer {
      margin-top: 72px;
      padding-top: 28px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--text-mute);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    footer .footer-block {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    footer .footer-block:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    footer .footer-label {
      color: var(--text-sub);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 11px;
      margin-right: 6px;
    }
    footer .sources {
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }
    footer .disclosure {
      color: var(--text-mute);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 8px;
    }
    footer .footer-issue {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-feature-settings: 'tnum';
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    /* Mobile adjustments */
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      body { padding: 0 16px 60px; font-size: 15px; }
      header { padding-top: 44px; margin-bottom: 36px; }
      header h1 { font-size: 56px; }
      .section-header h2 { font-size: 21px; }
      .section-header { padding: 16px 18px; }
      .section-body { padding: 4px 18px 8px; }
      .article h3 { font-size: 17px; }
      .must-read .item h3 { font-size: 15px; }
      .must-read { margin: 0 -16px 36px; padding: 22px 18px; }
    }

    /* ================================================
       FX D + E 조합 (KINETIC + BRUTALIST) — 항상 활성
       ================================================ */

    /* ── 헤더: D 글자 스플래시 + E 굵은 타이포 ── */
    body[data-fx="de"] header h1 { font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.04em; }
    body[data-fx="de"] header h1 .char {
      display: inline-block;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(80px) rotate(-8deg);
      animation: fxDE-char 0.8s cubic-bezier(.2,1,.3,1) forwards;
      animation-delay: calc(var(--i, 0) * 0.07s);
    }
    @keyframes fxDE-char { to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) rotate(0); } }

    /* ── 악센트 바: E 대각선 스트라이프 + D 가로 스윕 ── */
    body[data-fx="de"] .accent-bar {
      transform-origin: left;
      transform: scaleX(0);
      animation: fxDE-bar 0.7s cubic-bezier(.7,0,.3,1) 1.1s forwards;
    }
    @keyframes fxDE-bar { to { transform: scaleX(1); } }

    /* ── 섹션: D 줌인 — CSS keyframe 로 JS 의존 없이 자동 재생 ── */
    body[data-fx="de"] .section {
      transform: scale(0.94);
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fxDE-section-in 0.7s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1) 0.1s forwards;
    }
    @keyframes fxDE-section-in {
      to { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
    }

    /* ── 기사 카드: D 슬라이드 진입 + E 지그재그 미세 회전 + invert 호버 ── */
    body[data-fx="de"] .article {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-60px) rotate(-0.8deg);
      animation: fxDE-article-in 0.55s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1) 0.2s forwards;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
    }
    @keyframes fxDE-article-in {
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0) rotate(-0.25deg); }
    }
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:nth-of-type(even) {
      animation-name: fxDE-article-in-even;
    }
    @keyframes fxDE-article-in-even {
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0) rotate(0.25deg); }
    }
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:nth-of-type(2) { animation-delay: 0.28s; }
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:nth-of-type(3) { animation-delay: 0.36s; }
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover {
      background: var(--accent);
      transform: translateX(-8px) rotate(0);
      transition-duration: 0.2s;
    }
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover h3,
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover h3 a,
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover .meta,
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover .meta span,
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover .meta .dot,
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover .meta .score,
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover .tags,
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover .tags span,
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover .summary,
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover .why,
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover .why strong,
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover .link { color: var(--bg); }
    body[data-fx="de"] .article:hover .why {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      border-left-color: var(--bg);
    }

    /* ── 꼭 알아야 할 뉴스: D 순차 등장 (E 엠버 블록은 베이스 CSS에서 적용) ── */
    body[data-fx="de"] .must-read .item {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      animation: fxDE-item 0.65s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1) forwards;
    }
    body[data-fx="de"] .must-read .item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.12s; }
    body[data-fx="de"] .must-read .item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.26s; }
    body[data-fx="de"] .must-read .item:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.40s; }
    body[data-fx="de"] .must-read .item:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.54s; }
    body[data-fx="de"] .must-read .item:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.68s; }
    @keyframes fxDE-item { to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

    /* 접근성: prefers-reduced-motion 사용자에 대한 애니메이션 비활성 */
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      body[data-fx="de"] *, body[data-fx="de"] *::before, body[data-fx="de"] *::after {
        animation-duration: 0.001s !important;
        animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
        transition-duration: 0.001s !important;
      }
      body[data-fx="de"] .article,
      body[data-fx="de"] .section,
      body[data-fx="de"] .must-read .item,
      body[data-fx="de"] header h1 .char,
      body[data-fx="de"] .accent-bar {
        opacity: 1 !important;
        transform: none !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body data-fx="de">

  <header>
    <h1>
      <span class="line">{{ hero_title_line1 }}</span>
      <span class="line">{{ hero_title_line2 }}</span>
    </h1>
    <div class="meta-line">
      <span>{{ generation_timestamp }}</span>
      <span class="dot">·</span>
      <span>{{ period_label }}</span>
      <span class="dot">·</span>
      <span class="issue">ISSUE #{{ issue_number }}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="accent-bar"></div>
    {% if trend_hashtags %}
    <div class="trending">
      <span class="label">오늘의 트렌드</span>
      {% for tag in trend_hashtags[:8] %}
      <span class="tag"># {{ tag }}</span>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </header>

  {% if must_know %}
  <section class="must-read" aria-label="꼭 알아야 할 뉴스">
    <h2>꼭 알아야 할 뉴스</h2>
    {% for article in must_know %}
    <div class="item">
      <h3><a href="{{ article.original_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ article.title }}</a></h3>
      <div class="meta">{{ article.source }} · {{ article.published_at_display }} · <span class="score">점수 {{ "%.1f"|format(article.relevance_score) }}/10</span></div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  {% for section in sections %}
  {% if section.articles %}
  <section class="section" aria-label="{{ section.title }}">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>{{ section.title }}</h2>
      <span class="count">{{ section.articles|length }}건</span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      {% for article in section.articles %}
      <article class="article">
        <h3><a href="{{ article.original_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ article.title }}</a></h3>
        <div class="meta">
          <span>{{ article.source }}</span><span class="dot">·</span>
          <span>{{ article.published_at_display }}</span><span class="dot">·</span>
          <span class="score">점수 {{ "%.1f"|format(article.relevance_score) }}/10</span>
        </div>
        {% if article.keywords %}
        <div class="tags">
          {% for kw in article.keywords %}<span># {{ kw }}</span>{% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if article.insights and article.extraction_reason %}
        <details class="why-insights">
          <summary class="why"><strong>추출 이유</strong>{{ article.extraction_reason }}<span class="expand-hint" aria-hidden="true">▾</span></summary>
          <div class="insights-body">
            <div class="insight" data-axis="ripple">
              <h4>{{ article.insights.ripple.icon }} {{ article.insights.ripple.title }}</h4>
              <p>{{ article.insights.ripple.text }}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="insight" data-axis="history">
              <h4>{{ article.insights.history.icon }} {{ article.insights.history.title }}</h4>
              <p>{{ article.insights.history.text }}</p>
            </div>
            {% for b in article.insights.bonus %}
            <div class="insight" data-axis="{{ b.type }}">
              <h4>{{ b.icon }} {{ b.title }}</h4>
              <p>{{ b.text }}</p>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </details>
        {% elif article.extraction_reason %}
        <div class="why"><strong>추출 이유</strong>{{ article.extraction_reason }}</div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if article.ai_summary %}
        <div class="summary">{{ article.ai_summary }}</div>
        {% endif %}
        <a href="{{ article.original_url }}" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">원문 보기 →</a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
  {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-block">
      <span class="footer-label">생성시각</span>{{ generation_timestamp }}
    </div>
    <div class="footer-block sources">
      <span class="footer-label">RSS 출처</span>{{ rss_sources|join(" · ") }}
    </div>
    <div class="footer-block disclosure">
      본 리포트는 Claude Opus 4.7이 RSS 원문을 분석해 생성합니다. 사실관계는 각 원문에서 확인하세요.
    </div>
    <div class="footer-block footer-issue">
      ISSUE #{{ issue_number }}
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    (function () {
      // Split header h1 into char spans (for FX D kinetic reveal)
      let charCounter = 0;
      document.querySelectorAll('header h1 .line').forEach((line) => {
        const text = line.textContent;
        line.innerHTML = Array.from(text).map((ch) => {
          const idx = charCounter++;
          const safe = ch === ' ' ? '&nbsp;' : ch;
          return `<span class="char" style="--i:${idx}">${safe}</span>`;
        }).join('');
      });

      // IntersectionObserver adds .fx-in on scroll (needed by D slide/zoom)
      const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
        entries.forEach(e => {
          if (e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('fx-in');
        });
      }, { threshold: 0.12, rootMargin: '0px 0px -8% 0px' });
      document.querySelectorAll('.article, .section').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
    })();
  </script>

</body>
</html>
